{"tid":2459262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緬甸七歲女童被軍方擊斃 在父親懷中離世","createTime":"2021-03-24T05:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T05:41:10.000Z","uid":391580,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c27090d3f569f0c6bd5497fdc1394a07586e949c","tid":2459262,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:01:56.000Z","msg":"緬甸中部城市曼德勒近日不斷發生軍警血腥鎮壓事件，7歲女童欽苗奇（Ma Khin Myo Chit）周二在寓所被士兵射殺。當地居民表示，事發時警員和士兵向街頭圍觀的市民開槍，遇害女童則是在軍方搜屋時遭槍擊身亡，她的19歲兄長亦被軍方毒打及帶走。<br />\n<br />\n曼德勒周二共有3人被軍警殺害，令全國自2月初軍方發動政變後的死亡人數增至260人。緬甸軍方近日持續在曼德勒市中心附近的昌妙達齊（Chanmyathazi）區鎮壓示威，清走民眾設置的路障，又多次向人群開槍。<br />\n<br />\n軍警周二清場時再次向街上眾人開槍，遇害女童欽苗奇一家當日下午被士兵登門搜查，更有士兵向她開槍，欽苗奇最後死於父親懷中，她的兄長亦被捕。從網上流傳照片可見，年僅7歲的欽苗奇滿身是血，腹部可見有傷痕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210324/OOJGNXCKKZFC3FNSV3SFRHZ7JE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210324%2FOOJGNXCKKZFC3FNSV3SFRHZ7JE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=bXICEjaVmsGxuRkiXhyD2A5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=a7bb75d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210324%2FOOJGNXCKKZFC3FNSV3SFRHZ7JE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=f04e5c6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210324/OOJGNXCKKZFC3FNSV3SFRHZ7JE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"32dff1d0b43f4c3d48ee6189aa01a4ebdb1dc02a","tid":2459262,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:04:03.000Z","msg":"死共匪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal